Package: geolink
Title: Swiss Army Knife for Linking Spatial Identifers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonas", "Lieth", , "jonas.lieth@gesis.org", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3451-3176"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive set of tools for linking and
    enriching tabular data with spatial geometries using a variety of spatial
    identifiers, including various country codes, NUTS, LAU, FIPS, INSPIRE, and
    others. Supports guessing unknown spatial identifiers. Allows for the
    creation of reproducible linking workflows by registering custom and
    portable guessing, parsing, and linking functions.
